Message: The RD Licensing database file is not valid. This file has been renamed to '{param1}'; and the license server will start up with an empty database file. To resolve this issue; ensure that the required groups are granted the correct permissions to the LServer directory; and then reinstall the licenses. If the problem persists; rebuild the RD Licensing database and call the Microsoft Clearinghouse. When you call the Clearinghouse; ensure that your License Purchase Agreement information is readily available.
